title: Watch: BABYMONSTER Drops Fierce Dance Performance Video For “BATTER UP”
summary: YG Entertainment’s new girl group BABYMONSTER has revealed the full choreography for “BATTER UP”!

title: Watch: ITZY Announces Comeback Schedule And 2024 World Tour With 1st Teaser And Track List For “BORN TO BE”
summary: On December 4 at midnight KST, ITZY officially announced their plans for their highly-anticipated January comeback and 2024 world tour.

title: Watch: IVE Takes 5th Win And Triple Crown For “Baddie” On “Inkigayo”; Performances By ENHYPEN, SEVENTEEN’s Dino, And More
summary: On the December 3 episode of SBS’s “Inkigayo,” the candidates for first place were THE BOYZ’s “WATCH IT,” aespa’s “Drama,” and IVE’s “Baddie.” IVE ultimately took the win with a total of 5,731 points.

title: Watch: Performances From Melon Music Awards 2023
summary: On December 2, the Melon Music Awards 2023 held an exciting show featuring performances by NCT DREAM, aespa, IVE, NewJeans, SHINee, STAYC, RIIZE, ZEROBASEONE, BOYNEXTDOOR, Lee Young Ji, KISS OF LIFE, imase, and Silica Gel.

title: Watch: Super Junior’s Donghae, Lee Seol, EXID’s Jeonghwa, And More Face Relatable Love Life Problems In “Between Him And Her” Teaser
summary: “Between Him and Her” is a realistic romance drama about the love and boredom that coexist for long-term couples. Super Junior’s Donghae will star as Jung Hyun Sung, a fashion designer who is is about to celebrate his seventh anniversary with his girlfriend Han Sung Ok (Lee Seol).

title: Watch: THE BOYZ Takes 1st Win For “WATCH IT” On “Music Bank”; Performances By ATEEZ, ENHYPEN, And More
summary: On the December 1 episode of KBS 2TV’s “Music Bank,” the candidates for first place were THE BOYZ’s “WATCH IT” and ZEROBASEONE’s “CRUSH.” THE BOYZ ultimately took the win with a total of 7,511 points.

title: Watch: Lee Young Ae Tightens Discipline As The New Conductor Of An Orchestra In “Maestra: Strings Of Truth” Teaser
summary: tvN’s “Maestra: Strings of Truth” has unveiled a new teaser and character posters!

title: Watch: “EXchange” (“Transit Love”) Announces Season 3 Premiere Date With 1st Preview
summary: On December 1, TVING’s hit dating show “EXchange” (also known as “Transit Love”) officially revealed the premiere date—and first sneak peek—of its highly-anticipated third season.

title: Watch: ONE PACT Announces Official Fandom Name Ahead Of Debut
summary: On November 29, ONE PACT—a new five-member boy group made up of former “Boys Planet” contestants—released a video of the members announcing their official fandom name ahead of their debut.

title: Watch: Performances From 2023 MAMA Awards Day 2
summary: On November 29, the second night of the 2023 MAMA Awards was held at Japan’s Tokyo Dome.
